text.header1: Angmaumajut turrarvikhat Qajangnaittumik imaalu Atirnik uqaqhimaittumik aturlutit Kasm Angmaqtut-Avaliingaaqtitauniq.
text.header2: Kasm Angmaumayuq Avaliingaaqtitaunikkut qiniqhiadjut hivituqyuumiyuq tunihiyuq ihuaqtumik naqilugu piyakhaq angmariangani qaritauyaliqiviit Havagvingni ungahiktumi qiniqhiayunun. Una ayungnaituq uvalu ihuaqtumik angmaumayumik/qayangnaitumik URLsnik uvaluuniin pihimayaangani hiamitailinikkut. Talvanga qaritauyaliqidjutitigun aulalirman iluani avaliqangitunik havakvingmi qiniqhiayukharnik, aulatitihimaitumik nunalaani qaritauyarni, qayangnairutikharnik atiqangitumiklu ilaulukaagianganik qaritauyaliqidjutitigun.

title.tooltip1: Angmarniaqtuq URL-mik nutaami Havagvingmi, una Cast Key-mik qanuriliurutikhaq tadja atuqtaujumi aulniaqtun havagvingmi
title.tooltip2: Angmakhigumik titiraqhimayunik talvani Kasm Workspacesmi katimadjutikharnik kihiani auladjutikhangit ihuagiyaugumi URLngit pigiaqtitiniaqtun qiniqhiayukharnik ingniqutikharnik
title.tooltip3: Angmaqtirnikkut titirarvikhat Havagvingmi himmauhirumagupkit havagvik qaangiutikpat Havagvingmun (Naunaijarlugu ikajurutikhat atuqpagait RegExp-kut piqarhuni /angiklijunun/g)
